---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Philosophy | Elevate With Andy">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    
    <!-- Hero Header Narrative -->
    <header class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#7a7480] uppercase block mb-3">About the Practice</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-wide text-[#1e1b21] uppercase">Resilience in Motion</h1>
      <div class="w-12 h-px bg-[#7a7480]/30 mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </header>

    <!-- Editorial Core Story Content -->
    <article class="space-y-8 text-base text-[#1e1b21] font-light leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Elevate With Andy was founded as an intentional space to bridge the worlds of precision alignment, deep athletic conditioning, and expressive artistry. The practice is centered on a simple truth: sustainable physical freedom begins by cultivating a body that moves with depth, structural balance, and grace.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Rather than chasing superficial strain or temporary exhaustion, classes focus on somatic mechanics—decompressing joint segments, strengthening pelvic stabilizers, and mapping healthy kinetic patterns that translate directly into your daily life.
      </p>

      <!-- Mid-Page Callout Block -->
      <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-[#7a7480] pl-6 my-10 italic text-[#7a7480] font-normal">
        "True physical conditioning honors the architecture of the body, cultivating deep postural awareness so you can transition gracefully through load, gravity, and speed."
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        Whether you are working through the targeted core tracking of Classical Pilates, exploring the expansive lines of Ballet technique, or resetting joint mechanics through Functional Movement props, the goal remains identical: building resilience.
      </p>
    </article>

    <!-- The Three Pillars Detail Shelves -->
    <section class="mt-20 space-y-12">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-[#7a7480] uppercase border-b border-neutral-100 pb-2">The Modalities</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1e1b21] uppercase tracking-wide">01 / Functional Movement</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7480] font-light mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Decompressing overactive paraspinal muscle lines, optimizing joint track planes, and using targeted texturing tools—like the Franklin Method—to transform your everyday motor mechanics and somatic feedback loops.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1e1b21] uppercase tracking-wide">02 / Pilates Practice</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7480] font-light mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Deeply accessing internal core networks, refining spinal flexions, and introducing structural alignment anchors to ensure your muscular framework operates with perfect, protective balance symmetry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1e1b21] uppercase tracking-wide">03 / Ballet Artistry</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7480] font-light mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Refining long kinetic extensions, building dynamic center balance control, and exploring technical athletic coordination to build a graceful presence that moves cleanly across all planes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Connect / Call to Action Block -->
    <section class="mt-20 pt-12 border-t border-neutral-100 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-light uppercase tracking-wide text-[#1e1b21]">Join the Practice</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-[#7a7480] font-light mt-2 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Explore targeted video tutorials or read through our somatic research files directly inside the interface portal.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-6">
        <a href="/videos" class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-[#1e1b21] hover:bg-[#7a7480] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded transition-colors shadow-sm">
          Browse Videos
        </a>
        <a href="/LivingNotebook" class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase border border-[#7a7480]/30 hover:border-[#1e1b21] text-[#1e1b21] px-6 py-3 rounded transition-colors">
          Open Notebook
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
